{"tid":181861,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"成班酸葡萄屌人地ig賣廣告","createTime":"2017-04-01T02:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T06:59:42.000Z","uid":93485,"like":68,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"25ddf8104a4ef5781189d2f206122046dd42f219","tid":181861,"uid":93485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:17:46.000Z","msg":"柒係柒左啲 但銅鑼灣日撚日擺街叫人打卡送乜柒個排曬長龍啦 有老有嫩 <br />\n跟本呢啲野著數大把人想拎<br />\n唔見你屌<br />\n<br />\n而家出左post有錢收有野送 有人做有幾咁奇<br />\n屌人柒還屌人柒<br />\n成班唔撚抵得又另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平心而論啦 學生哥upload<br />\n<br />\n張相有幾舊水<br />\n一日糧啦屌<br />\n比你都簡up張相啦<br />\non9<br />\n成班酸葡萄 其實比你都會up啦 <br />\n不過自己無就屌鳩人<br />\n<br />\n屌鳩我囉 我唔似你地咁撚易葡萄人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/100229_9aa6c062847c2a88ae9ea754663d2725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F100229_9aa6c062847c2a88ae9ea754663d2725.jpg&h=0f3bd666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正評：up張相unun腳收幾舊水<br />\n負皮：寧願番一日工"},{"pid":"03e308878f67afccd1124889028705ace9b0267d","tid":181861,"uid":34965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"腦細唔gur叫你上嚟做打手呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3fbcf7b0c8a9bfebfa46a36a784e5263a12972","tid":181861,"uid":93485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:24:40.000Z","msg":"好似中學咁 酸就係度瓜瓜嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0434ec7438590b41579f56b3ee712c67ac6731","tid":181861,"uid":93485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腦細唔gur叫你上嚟做打手呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n葡萄人地係咁易出個post又